                <mxCell id="legend" value="Legend.&#xa;Heavy green / amber arrows: the file boundary (noodle writes → file → collector tails). The single interchange between the two processes.&#xa;Thin grey: OTLP ingress from non-noodle producers. Green to the-telemetry-backend: OTLP egress after enrichment.&#xa;noodle has no OTLP code. The collector is a separate process; its repository, name, and deployment are out of this ADR." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#444444;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=4" parent="1" vertex="1">
